OL,3,CLord Mandelson released on bail
OL,4,Cpending further investigation
OL,6,FLord Peter Mandelson has been released
OL,7,Fon bail after his arrest on suspicion
OL,8,Fof misconduct in public office, the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,11,FThe former Labour minister has been
OL,12,Faccused of passing sensitive
OL,13,Finformation onto paedophile financier
OL,14,FJeffrey Epstein during his time as
OL,15,Fbusiness secretary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
