OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1771909410
OL,3,CLord Mandelson released on bail
OL,4,Cpending further investigation
OL,6,FIn a statement issued just after 2am
OL,7,Fon Tuesday, a spokesperson for the
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police said: "A 72-year-
OL,9,Fold man arrested on suspicion of
OL,10,Fmisconduct in public office has been
OL,11,Freleased on bail pending further
OL,12,Finvestigation.
OL,14,F"He was arrested at an address in
OL,15,FCamden on Monday, 23 February and was
OL,16,Ftaken to a London police station for
OL,17,Finterview.
OL,19,F"This follows search warrants at two
OL,20,Faddresses in the Wiltshire and Camden
OL,21,Fareas.
OL,26,@pD@[OUvD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
