OL,3,CLord Mandelson released on bail
OL,4,Cpending further investigation
OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrats will, meanwhile,
OL,7,Fseek to force the public release of
OL,8,Ffiles relating to Andrew Mountbatten-
OL,9,FWindsor's appointment as a trade
OL,10,Fenvoy, as the former prince also faces
OL,11,Faccusations of sharing sensitive
OL,12,Finformation with Epstein while in the
OL,13,Frole.
OL,15,FFootage showed Lord Mandelson being
OL,16,Fled out of his house by a plain
OL,17,Fclothes police officer on Monday and
OL,18,Fthe Metropolitan Police later said the
OL,19,F72-year-old was taken to a London
OL,20,Fpolice station for interview.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
