OL,3,CLord Mandelson released on bail
OL,4,Cpending further investigation
OL,6,FTwo of his properties were previously
OL,7,Fsearched by police in connection with
OL,8,Fthe allegations, which surfaced
OL,9,Ffollowing the US Department of
OL,10,FJustice's document dump related to
OL,11,FEpstein last month.
OL,13,FAs part of the so-called Epstein
OL,14,Ffiles, emails from 2009 appear to show
OL,15,FLord Mandelson pass on an assessment
OL,16,Fby Gordon Brown's adviser of potential
OL,17,Fpolicy measures including an "asset
OL,18,Fsales plan".
OL,26,@yD@^OUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
