OL,3,CLord Mandelson released on bail
OL,4,Cpending further investigation
OL,6,FHe also appeared to discuss a tax on
OL,7,Fbankers' bonuses and confirm an
OL,8,Fimminent bailout package for the euro
OL,9,Fthe day before it was announced in
OL,10,F2010.
OL,12,FThe emails appeared to be sent to
OL,13,FEpstein after he became a convicted
OL,14,Fsex offender.
OL,16,FIt is understood the Crown Prosecution
OL,17,FService is yet to offer any early
OL,18,Finvestigative advice in relation to
OL,19,Fthe allegations against Lord Mandelson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
