OL,3,CLord Mandelson released on bail
OL,4,Cpending further investigation
OL,6,FThe Cabinet Office previously referred
OL,7,Fmaterial to police in connection with
OL,8,Fthe probe into Lord Mandelson after an
OL,9,Finitial review of the Epstein files
OL,10,Fsuggested "safeguards were
OL,11,Fcompromised".
OL,13,FThe arrest came shortly after MPs were
OL,14,Ftold the first tranche of documents
OL,15,Frelated to Lord Mandelson's
OL,16,Fappointment as US ambassador is
OL,17,Fexpected to be released in early March.
OL,26,@rD@KOUsD@LO]
