OL,3,CLord Mandelson released on bail
OL,4,Cpending further investigation
OL,6,FChief Secretary to the Prime Minister,
OL,7,FDarren Jones, said some of the
OL,8,Fcorrespondence between Downing Street
OL,9,Fand the peer will be delayed "because
OL,10,Fof the Metropolitan Police interest".
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister previously said the
OL,13,Ffiles will prove Lord Mandelson lied
OL,14,Fduring the vetting process before
OL,15,Ftaking on the ambassador role.
OL,26,@qD@^OUrD@dO]
