OL,3,CLord Mandelson released on bail
OL,4,Cpending further investigation
OL,6,FFollowing the release of the Epstein
OL,7,Ffiles, Lord Mandelson said he has "no
OL,8,Frecollection" of receiving payments
OL,9,Ftotalling 75,000 dollars (about
OL,10,F#55,000) from Epstein between 2003 and
OL,11,F2004 as bank details in the documents
OL,12,Findicated.
OL,14,FEpstein is also said to have paid for
OL,15,Fan osteopathy course for Lord
OL,16,FMandelson's husband, Reinaldo Avila Da
OL,17,FSilva, in 2009, at the time the
OL,18,Fgovernment was dealing with the
OL,19,Ffinancial crisis.
OL,26,@oD@cOUpD@MO]
