OL,3,CLord Mandelson released on bail
OL,4,Cpending further investigation
OL,6,FLord Mandelson's arrest comes days
OL,7,Fafter Andrew was taken into custody on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of misconduct in public
OL,9,Foffice.
OL,11,FThe former prince was released under
OL,12,Finvestigation.
OL,14,FDespite being stripped of his title
OL,15,Flast year, the former duke of York is
OL,16,Fstill eighth in line to the throne,
OL,17,Fand an Act of Parliament would be
OL,18,Frequired to remove Andrew and prevent
OL,19,Fhim from ever becoming king.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
