OL,6,FThe motion will call for the release
OL,7,Fof papers relating to Andrew's
OL,8,Fappointment to the post, including any
OL,9,Fvetting and any correspondence from
OL,10,FLord Mandelson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
